     Src/Tests/Sigs/si64.sig Src/Tests/Sigs/sih.sig
     Src/Tests/cmpsig.f Src/Tests/do.sh Src/sig.f

    modified files:
     Docs/siesta.ind Docs/siesta.tex Src/Makefile
     Src/Tests/Makefile Src/Tests/Outs/si.out Src/Tests/si/makefile
